sections.heading: Officers Retirement Act, how cited; applicability
sections.text: Sections 16-1001 to 16-1019 shall be known and may be cited as the Police Officers Retirement Act and shall apply to all police officers of a city of the first class.SourceLaws 1983, LB 237, ยง 1;Laws 2012, LB1082, ยง 1.
